# One-off local data imports (real member PII, e.g. club roster spreadsheets) —
# never committed, including the import script itself. Anchored to repo root
# (leading slash) — an unanchored "Data/" also matched frontend/src/data/,
# silently keeping countries.js/currencies.js out of every commit ever since
# they were added (worked locally since gitignore doesn't delete files, but
# they never reached GitHub — broke the Render production build).
/Data/

